gba honoured by Football Writers |date=25 January 2015 |publisher=[[Chelsea FC]] |accessdate=27 January 2014}}</ref>\n*[[Golden Foot]]: 2013<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goldenfoot.com/en/winners/item/418-didier-drogba-2013.html |title=Didier Drogba (2013) |date=16 October 2013 |publisher=[[Golden Foot]] |accessdate=16 August 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140710212047/http://www.goldenfoot.com/en/winners/item/418-didier-drogba-2013.html |archivedate=10 July 2014 }}</ref>\n*[[Ivory Coast Player of the Year]]: 2006, 2007, 2012<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldfootball.net/fussballer_des_jahres/elfenbeinkueste/ |title=Player of the year \u00bb Ivory Coast |publisher=Worldfootball.net |accessdate=16 August 2014}}</ref>\n*[[Troph\u00e9es UNFP du football#Goal of the Year|Ligue 1 Goal of the Year]]: [[Troph\u00e9es UNFP du football#Goal of the Year|2003\u201304]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportpalmares.eu/Trophees-UNFP-Oscars-du-football,246.html?lang=fr |title=Palmar\u00e8s Troph\u00e9es UNFP \u2013 Oscars du football \u2013 \"Le plus beau but de Ligue 1\" (vote du public) |language=French |publisher=Sport Palmares |accessdate=16 August 2014}}</ref>\n*[[UNFP Player of the Month|Ligue 1 Player of the Month]]: January 2004, May 2004{{citation needed|date=April 2019}}\n*[[Troph\u00e9es UNFP du football#Player of the Year|Ligue 1 Player of the Year]]: [[Troph\u00e9es UNFP du football#Player of the Year|2003\u201304]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportpalmares.eu/Trophees-UNFP-Oscars-du-football.html?lang=fr |title=Palmar\u00e8s Troph\u00e9es UNFP \u2013 Oscars du football \u2013 Meilleur joueur de Ligue 1 |language=French |publisher=Sport Palmares |accessdate=16 August 2014}}</ref>\n*[[Troph\u00e9es UNFP du football#2004|Ligue 1 Team of the Year]]: [[Troph\u00e9es UNFP du football#2004|2003\u201304]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportpalmares.eu/Trophees-UNFP-Oscars-du-football,239.html?lang=fr |title=Palmar\u00e8s Troph\u00e9es UNF