eague|2006\u201307]],<ref>{{cite news |title=Drogba collects Golden Boot award |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/chelsea/6664459.stm |work=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|date=18 May 2007 |accessdate=7 October 2013 }}</ref> [[2009\u201310 Premier League|2009\u201310]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Terry calls for fresh investment to build on success |url=http://www.irishtimes.com/sport/terry-calls-for-fresh-investment-to-build-on-success-1.663646 |date=11 May 2010 |accessdate=7 October 2013 |newspaper=The Irish Times }} '''{{subscription required}}</ref>\n*[[PFA Team of the Year]]: [[PFA Team of the Year (2000s)#FA Premier League 8|2006\u201307 Premier League]],<ref name=2007PFA /> [[PFA Team of the Year (2010s)#Premier League|2009\u201310 Premier League]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8643305.stm |title=Rooney is PFA player of the year |publisher=BBC Sport |date=25 April 2010 |accessdate=27 April 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Time Top 100]]: 2010<ref>{{cite web|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1984685_1984864,00.html |title=The 2010 TIME 100 |date=29 April 2010 |work=[[Time (magazine)|TIME]] |accessdate=16 August 2014}}</ref>\n*[[Milliyet Sports Awards#Footballer Of The Year|Turkish Footballer of the Year]]: 2013<ref>{{cite web|url=http://skorer.milliyet.com.tr/yilin-sporcusu-arda-turan/-/detay/1825340/default.htm |title=Y\u0131l\u0131n sporcusu Arda Turan |language=Turkish |date=21 January 2014 |work=[[Milliyet]] |accessdate=16 August 2014}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Best Player in Europe Award]]: [[UEFA Best Player in Europe Award|7th place 2012]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Iniesta, Messi, Ronaldo up for Best Player Award|url=http://www.uefa.org/uefa-best-player-award/news/newsid=1842518.html|accessdate=15 November 2015|publisher=UEFA|date=14 August 2012}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Champions League Final]] Man of the Match: [[2012 UEFA Champions League Final|2012]]<ref name=\"player_rater\">{{cite web |title=Player Rater \u