11|title=France's Cesar Awards: Winners List (Updating Live)|last= Roxborough|first=Scott|website= [[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=February 28, 2020|accessdate=February 28, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229004105/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/amp/lists/cesar-awards-2020-winners-list-full-1276711|archive-date=February 29, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Chicago Film Critics Association]]\n| December 14, 2019\n| [[Chicago Film Critics Association Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n| Joaquin Phoenix\n| {{Nominated}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2019-chicago-film-critics-association-cfca-nominations|title=The 2019 Chicago Film Critics Association (CFCA) Nominations|last=Neglia|first=Matt|website=Next Best Picture|date=December 12, 2019|accessdate=December 12, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212161102/https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2019-chicago-film-critics-association-cfca-nominations|archive-date=December 12, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><br/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://chicagofilmcritics.org/blog/2019cfca|title=Parasite, Little Women Lead 2019 Chicago Film Critics Awards, Winning Four Wins Each|last=Chicago Film Critics Association Editors|website=[[Chicago Film Critics Association]]|date=December 14, 2019|accessdate=December 15, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215112121/https://chicagofilmcritics.org/blog/2019cfca|archive-date=December 15, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Cinema Audio Society Awards]]\n| January 25, 2020\n| [[Cinema Audio Society Award for Outstanding Achievement in Sound Mixing for a Motion Picture \u2013 Live Action|Motion Picture \u2013 Live Action]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |''Joker''\n| {{Nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/cas-awards-2019-nominations-joker-frozen-2-game-of-thrones-fleabag-cinema-audio-society-1202805010/|t