play|Best Adapted Screenplay]]\n| Scott Silver, Todd Phillips\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Cinematography|Best Cinematography]]\n| Lawrence Sher\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Costume Design|Best Production Design]]\n| Mark Friedberg, Kris Moran\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Makeup|Best Hair and Makeup]]\n|''Joker''\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Score|Best Score]]\n| Hildur Gu\u00f0nad\u00f3ttir\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Dallas\u2013Fort Worth Film Critics Association]]\n| December 16, 2019\n| [[Dallas\u2013Fort Worth Film Critics Association Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n| Joaquin Phoenix\n| {{Runner-up}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dfwcritics.com/dfw-film-critics-pick-1917-as-best-film-of-2019/|title=DFW FILM CRITICS PICK \"1917\" AS BEST FILM OF 2019|last=Jorgenson|first=Todd|website=[[Dallas\u2013Fort Worth Film Critics Association]]|date=December 16, 2019|accessdate=January 3, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216161254/https://dfwcritics.com/dfw-film-critics-pick-1917-as-best-film-of-2019/|archive-date=December 16, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[David di Donatello Awards]]\n| April 3, 2020\n| [[David di Donatello for Best Foreign Film|Best Foreign Film]]\n|''Joker''\n| {{Nominated}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ansa.it/english/news/lifestyle/arts/2020/02/18/parasite-wins-best-foreign-film-david_63093fd3-38c0-4dce-b70f-76ec8697ddc9.html|title=CANDIDATI PREMI DAVID DI DONATELLO 2020|last=|first=|website=[[Agenzia Nazionale Stampa Associata|ANSA]]|date=February 18, 2020|accessdate=February 18, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218145036/http://www.ansa.it/english/news/lifestyle/arts/2020/02/18/parasite-wins-best-foreign-film-david_63093fd3-38c0-4dce-b70f-76ec8697ddc9.html|archive-date=February 18, 2020|u