om/awards/2020-razzie-award-winners-cats/|archive-date=March 16, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"14\" scope=\"row\" | [[JoBlo.com#Golden Schmoes Awards|Golden Schmoes Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"14\" | February 7, 2020\n| Favorite Movie of the Year\n| {{Nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"14\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.joblo.com/movie-news/the-winners-of-the-19th-annual-golden-schmoes-are-announced|title=THE WINNERS OF THE 19TH ANNUAL GOLDEN SCHMOES ARE ANNOUNCED!|last=Shirey|first=Paul|website=[[JoBlo.com]]|date=February 7, 2020|accessdate=February 8, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Director of the Year\n| Todd Phillips\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| Best Screenplay of the Year\n| Todd Phillips, Scott Silver\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| Most Overrated Movie of the Year\n| rowspan=\"3\" |''Joker''\n| {{Runner-up}}\n|-\n| Trippiest Movie of the Year\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| Biggest Surprise of the Year\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Best Actor of the Year\n| Joaquin Phoenix\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Coolest Character of the Year\n| Joker/Arthur Fleck\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| Best Music in a Movie\t\n| Hildur Gu\u00f0nad\u00f3ttir\n| {{Runner-up}}\n|-\n| Favorite Movie Poster of the Year\n| rowspan=\"3\" |''Joker''\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| Best Trailer of the Year\n| {{Runner-up}}\n|-\n| Best DVD/Blu-Ray of the Year\t\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| Most Memorable Scene in a Movie\n| Murray Franklin Interview\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| Best Line of the Year\n| \"I used to think my life was a tragedy, but now I realize it's a comedy.\"\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Goldene Leinwand|Golden Screen Awards]]\n| October 10, 2019\n| Golden Screen\n| ''Joker''\n| {{Won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.goldene-leinwand.de/filme/joker/|title=Joker|last=Howard|first=|website=Goldene-leinwand|date=October 10, 2019|accessdate=October 10, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227141357/https://www.goldene-leinwand.de/filme/joker/|archive-date=Octob