9/12/sag-awards-nominations-list-film-tv-nominees-screen-actors-guild-1202806390/|title=SAG Awards Nominations: 'Bombshell', 'The Irishman', 'Once Upon A Time In Hollywood' Top Film List, 'Maisel,' 'Fleabag' Score In TV \u2013 Complete List Of Noms|last=Hipes|first=Patrick|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=December 11, 2019|accessdate=December 11, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211153707/https://deadline.com/2019/12/sag-awards-nominations-list-film-tv-nominees-screen-actors-guild-1202806390/|archive-date=December 11, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><br/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/sag-awards-live-blog-2020-screen-actors-guild-1202835488/|title=Deadline\u2019s SAG Awards Live Blog|last=Hammond|first=Pete|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=January 19, 2020|accessdate=January 20, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200120045203/https://deadline.com/2020/01/sag-awards-live-blog-2020-screen-actors-guild-1202835488/|archive-date=January 20, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Stunt Ensemble in a Motion Picture|Outstanding Performance by a Stunt Ensemble in a Motion Picture]]\n| The stunt ensemble of ''Joker''\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" scope=\"row\"| [[Seattle Film Critics Society]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"| December 16, 2019\n| Best Actor\n| Joaquin Phoenix\n| {{Nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"3\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2019-seattle-film-critics-society-sfcs-winners|title=The 2019 Seattle Film Critics Society (SFCS) Winners|last=Neglia|first=Matt|website=Next Best Picture|date=December 16, 2019|accessdate=December 16, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Original Score\n| Hildur Gu\u00f0nad\u00f3ttir\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| Best Villain of the Year\n| Joaquin Phoenix\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Society of Operating Cameramen|Society of Camera Operators]]\n| January 18, 2020\n| [[Society of Camera