\n| [[Warner Bros.]], JAX\n| {{Nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2019-golden-trailer-awards-complete-winners-list-1209264/item/best-show-golden-trailer-winners-2019-1214314|title='John Wick: Chapter 3 - Parabellum' Nabs Best in Show at 2019 Golden Trailer Awards|last=Howard|first=Annie|website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=May 29, 2019|accessdate=September 7, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191008065406/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2019-golden-trailer-awards-complete-winners-list-1209264/item/best-show-golden-trailer-winners-2019-1214314|archive-date=October 8, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Guild of Music Supervisors Awards]]\n| February 6, 2020\n| Best Music Supervision for Trailers\n| Anny Colvin\n| {{Won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/music/news/guild-of-music-supervisors-awards-winners-full-list-1203496186/amp/|title=Guild of Music Supervisors Awards: Regina Spektor, \u2018Euphoria\u2019 Among Winners (Full List)|last=Herman|first=James|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=February 7, 2020|accessdate=February 7, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207121710/https://variety.com/2020/music/news/guild-of-music-supervisors-awards-winners-full-list-1203496186/amp/|archive-date=February 7, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"row\"| [[Guinness World Records]]<!-- Do not remove! This is a credible award from the Guinness World Records, as supported by their website and the link provided-->\n| rowspan=\"2\" | December 9, 2019\n| First R-rated film to earn $1 billion\n| rowspan=\"4\" |''Joker''\n| {{Won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2019/12/frozen-2-smashes-box-office-record-joining-avengers-endgame-joker-and-more-601910/|title=Frozen 2 smashes box office record joining Avengers: Endgam